    <h1>XL Squid Stuffed Tomato Bar&#xAD;ley Risotto ($28)</h1>
    <h2></h2>
    <section>
        <a href="/singapore/the-straits-times/textview" title="The Straits Times">The Straits Times</a>
        - <a href="/singapore/the-straits-times/20200920/textview" title="The Straits Times - 2020-09-20"><time>2020-09-20</time></a>
        - <span>LIFE | FOOD &amp; DRINK</span>
        - <span role="byline"></span>
    </section>

    <p>The idea of stuff­ing a whole squid with bar­ley and grilling it sounds good. But the ex­e­cu­tion needs work.</p>
    <p>The prob­lem is that the bar­ley risotto is too wet and the way the fill­ing oozes out when you cut into the squid looks un­ap­peal­ing.</p>
    <p>The squid it­self is nicely done, but I would sug­gest a dif­fer­ent fill­ing.</p>

